    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Toy versions of dining, tea or coffee sets tailored to children or dolls. Older dinner sets are usually made of porcelain, earthenware or tin.. Modern versions are usually made of plastic.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
